377
00:31:13,990 --> 00:31:17,060
to not disappoint Xiao Douzi's hardship.

378
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:19,370
I will immediately mobilize the East Palace troops

379
00:31:19,370 --> 00:31:22,880
