380
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:26,890
[Reform from the Source]

381
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:31,870
I understand then.

382
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:34,900
When you passed the message,

383
00:31:34,900 --> 00:31:37,500
