478
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:50,440
That's why he must be

479
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:52,690
hidden in a secret place.

480
00:40:52,690 --> 00:40:56,380
These days, during the middle of the night,

481
00:40:56,380 --> 00:41:00,390
