482
00:41:00,390 --> 00:41:02,110
Really?

483
00:41:12,870 --> 00:41:14,290
[Peace within the Four Seas]

484
00:41:51,460 --> 00:41:55,090
Crown Prince Li Zhi intends to poison and kill His Majesty,

485
00:41:55,090 --> 00:41:59,680
